  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Runaway Train</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>I was one thousand stamens gliding through the air,</l>
          <l>sometimes I brought you flowers, now you don't seem to care.</l>
          <l>I was one thousand stamens in the air,</l>
          <l>now, now I'm flying, I'll be out of your hair.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>I'm going insane</l>
          <l>I'm the one leaving, </l>
          <l>but you're a runaway train.</l>
          <l>Runaway train.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>You, you were my water &amp; my dirt,</l>
          <l>roots that grow deep under shaking earth.</l>
          <l>Now, the winds are blowing somewhere else,</l>
          <l>and I'm just one thousand stamens out of your hair.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>I'm going insane</l>
          <l>I'm the one leaving, </l>
          <l>but you're a runaway train.</l>
          <l>Runaway train.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza" />
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>Runaway train...</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
